	**/

*include js -> https://github.com/mktvirtual/AvonBar/blob/master/avon.js (size: 5 kb)

*call init function
	avon.init(bgColor, lg, img, css);

*img = path to your images (ex.: http://www.avonmaquiagem.com.br/images) / put the folder "images_bar" in this path

*css = path to your css (ex.: http://www.avonmaquiagem.com.br/css) / put the folder "css_bar" in this path

*where color = hexadecimal string - use #000000

*lg = language(string) where:
				*'pt' = portugues only
<html>
	<head>
		<title>Title of the document</title>
	</head>
	<body>
		<div class="exemple">
			<script type="text/javascript" src="https://github.com/mktvirtual/AvonBar/blob/master/avon.js"></script>
			<script type="text/javascript" charset="utf-8">avon.init('#000000', 'pt', 'https://github.com/mktvirtual/AvonBar/tree/master', 'https://github.com/mktvirtual/AvonBar/tree/master');</script>			
		</div>
	</body>
</html>


